quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  2,189,"Iwo akukufunsani za miyezi yatsopano. Nena: “Zimenezi ndi zizindikiro za nyengo kwa anthu ndi nthawi ya Hajji. Ndipo sichilungamo kulowa m’nyumba podzera ku khomo la kumbuyo. Koma chilungamo ndi kuopa Mulungu. Motero lowani m’nyumba zanu kudzera m’makomo oyenera, ndipo opani Mulungu kuti mukhale opambana.”"
  2,190,"Menyanani nawo mu njira ya Mulungu, iwo amene amenyana nanu koma musapyole malire. Ndithudi Mulungu sakonda anthu oswa malamulo"
  2,191,"Ndipo muwaphe paliponse pamene muwapeza, ndipo achotseni m’malo monse m’mene adakuchotsani inu. Kusakhulupilira ndi kupembedza mafano ndi koipa kuposa kupha. Koma musamenyane nawo pa Mzikiti Woyera pokhapokha atakuputani. Koma ngati iwo akuputani, muwaphe. Imeneyo ndiyo mphotho ya anthu amene amakana choonadi"
  2,192,"Koma ngati iwo asiya, ndithudi Mulungu ndi okhululuka ndi wachisoni chosatha"
  2,193,"Menyanani nawo mpaka pamene kusakhulupilira ndi kupembedza mafano kutha ndiponso chipembedzo chikhala cha Mulungu yekha. Koma ngati iwo asiya, pasakhale chidani kupatula ndi anthu ochita zoipa"
  2,194,Mwezi Woyera ndi Mwezi Woyera ndipo zinthu zosaloledwa nazonso zimabwezeredwa. Ndipo aliyense amene akuputani mubwezereni molingana ndi mmene wachitira iye. Ndipo muopeni Mulungu ndipo dziwani kuti Mulungu ali pamodzi ndi iwo amene amalewa zoipa
  2,195,"Ndipoperekanim’njiraya Mulungundipomusadziponye nokha\tkuchionongeko.\tChitani\tzabwino.\tNdithudi Mulungu amakonda anthu ochita zabwino"
  2,196,"Kwaniritsani miyambo ya Hajji ndi Umra chifukwa cha Mulungu. Ndipo ngati mwatsekerezedwa, iphani, ngati nsembe, nyama zimene sizili zovuta kuzipeza ndipo musamete mitu yanu mpaka nyama zitafika pa malo ake ophera. Koma aliyense wa inu amene ndi wodwala kapena ali ndi vuto m’mutu mwake ayenera kudziombola posala kapena kupereka nsembe kapena kupha nyama. Ngati muli pa mtendere ndiponso wina wa inu aphatikiza Umra ndi Hajji, ayenera kupha nyama imene angaipeze mosavutikira kwambiri. Koma ngati sangathe kuipeza ayenera kusala masiku atatu pa nthawi ya Hajji ndi masiku asanu ndi awiri akabwerera kwawo; amenewo ndi masiku khumi okwana. Zimenezi ndi za iye amene banja lake silili pafupi ndi Mzikiti Woyera. Muopeni Mulungu. Ndipo dziwani kuti Mulungu amakhwimitsa chilango"
  2,197,"Nthawi ya Hajji ili ndi miyezi yake yodziwika. Aliyense amene afuna kupanga Hajji m’menemu sayenera kugona ndi mkazi wake kapena kuchitazoipakapenakukanganandianzakenthawiya Hajji. Ndipo chabwino chilichonse chimene muchita, Mulungu amachidziwa. Mutenge kamba wa paulendo, koma kamba wabwino ndi kuopa Mulungu. Motero ndiopeni Ine, inu anthu ozindikira"
  2,198,"Palibe mlandu kwa inu ngati inu mufuna zabwino kuchokera kwa Ambuye wanu. Motero pamene muchoka ku Arafat, kumbukirani Mulungu pafupi ndi chizindikiro choyera. Ndipo mukumbukeni Iye chifukwa Iye wakutsogolerani, popeza kale ndithudi inu mudali wa iwo amene adasokera"
  2,199,Ndipo pitani kumalo kumene anthu onse amapitako ndipo pemphani chikhululukiro cha Mulungu. Ndithudi Iye ndi wokhululukira ndi wachisoni chosatha
  2,200,"Ndipo pamene inu mukwaniritsa mapemphero anu a Hajji, kumbukirani Mulungu monga momwe mumakumbukira makolo anu kapena kuposa pamenepo. Ndipo pakati pawo pali iye amene amanena kuti: “Ambuye wathu! Tipatseni zabwino m’dziko lapansi!” Ndipo munthu wotere sadzakhala ndi gawo m’moyo umene uli nkudza"
  2,201,"Ndipo pakati pawo alipo wina wa iwo amene amati: “Ambuye wathu! Tipatseni zabwino m’dziko lino ndiponso zabwino m’dziko limene lili nkudza ndipo titetezeni ku chilango cha moto.”"
  2,202,Iwo adzakhala ndi gawo chifukwa cha ntchito zomwe amachita. Mulungu ndi wachangu powerengera